{"id": 2312, "genre": 1001, "title": "为了尝试做一个精致的人你都付出过哪些努力？", "description": "为了少洗碗而不摆盘不是我们精致人做的事。（题图来自：istock © Anna_Isaeva）", "record_count": 3562, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180502100637XNRPfl0rFQk48UBV.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-05-03T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 279296, "content": "有段时间心血来潮，做了一整个星期的的计划安排表，而且是精确到分钟的那种，结果实践不到三天就放弃了……?这算是很追求精致的一次行动了～", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 993991}, {"id": 281345, "content": "每天带水杯", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1340824}, {"id": 279298, "content": "撕掉脸上的每一小块死皮", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1093462}, {"id": 280579, "content": "睡觉穿睡衣", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1338237}, {"id": 280068, "content": "坚持健身，看书，学会花淡妆", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1132500}, {"id": 279301, "content": "把\"作\"变成习惯。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 748704}, {"id": 279302, "content": "坚持运动与看书，学习脸部护理与服装搭配，管理好自己的情绪", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1332856}, {"id": 279303, "content": "每天写日记", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1334000}, {"id": 279815, "content": "活着", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1159017}, {"id": 279304, "content": "怎么都得喝八杯水", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1274317}, {"id": 279305, "content": "泡咖啡 還必須是手沖那種⋯", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1317712}, {"id": 279306, "content": "每天坚持看好奇心日报", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1138907}, {"id": 279307, "content": "买了榨汁机，办了健身卡，睡前一定要你一点精油听听雨声。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1334018}, {"id": 279308, "content": "扔掉了百分之九十的东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1334024}, {"id": 279309, "content": "其实也没干嘛", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 928836}, {"id": 279310, "content": "不穿睡衣出门，即使只是下楼买点东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1332483}, {"id": 279311, "content": "化妆品 护肤", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1331803}, {"id": 279823, "content": "跑步减肥", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1311410}, {"id": 279312, "content": "随身携带纸巾湿巾马桶垫纸牙线眼药水漱口水酒精棉胃药止泻药创可贴。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 548295}, {"id": 279313, "content": "用叉子吃薯条", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1281331}, {"id": 279314, "content": "学化妆学搭配。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1321363}, {"id": 281362, "content": "爱生活\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1115496}, {"id": 281618, "content": "健身", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1343038}, {"id": 279315, "content": "汽车仪表台和后视镜不摆放任何东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 716159}, {"id": 282387, "content": "坚持跑步尽管讨厌的要命\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1346739}, {"id": 279316, "content": "每天坚持写读书笔记和工作总结！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1334058}, {"id": 280340, "content": "手机贴了膜 带了套", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1337452}, {"id": 279061, "content": "you are what you eat，饮食尽量戒糖少盐", "image": null, "praise_count": 275, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1333307}, {"id": 279317, "content": "在困也要按时起床，用洗面奶，爽肤水，乳液", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1327960}, {"id": 280085, "content": "赚钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1335815}, {"id": 280341, "content": "手机贴了膜带了套", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1337452}, {"id": 279062, "content": "外套按照颜色挂在衣柜里\n桌面图标按照颜色列两队\n手机图标按功能分组列队\n分组内的图标按颜色排列\n总之颜色和整齐非常重要\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 39, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1216775}, {"id": 279318, "content": "开始会在家具家私上投资了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1334066}, {"id": 279063, "content": "办了健身卡", "image": null, "praise_count": 181, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 747017}, {"id": 279319, "content": "洗……澡，\n\n呃，我会按彩虹色顺序穿衣服?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 191455}, {"id": 279064, "content": "学会用熨烫机", "image": null, "praise_count": 82, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1333310}, {"id": 279065, "content": "话很多时间在天猫\n选择衣服搭配上", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1325797}, {"id": 279321, "content": "必须要用一整个化妆台装下所有早上起床用到的化妆品和护肤品，然后花1个小时出门！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1279671}, {"id": 280345, "content": "分杯子喝不同液体……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1337470}, {"id": 279066, "content": "遇到好看的妹子的时候我都会主动精致一点", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 272909}, {"id": 279067, "content": "手机上有一天细小划痕，心里要难受半天。但……从来不爱带壳，喜欢抚摸设计的精致感", "image": null, "praise_count": 104, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 905876}, {"id": 279323, "content": "为了化个好妆提前半小时起床", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1152821}, {"id": 280091, "content": "不set头不出门，不允许一根碎发", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1224785}, {"id": 279068, "content": "随身携带纸巾湿巾牙线棒", "image": null, "praise_count": 157, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1184394}, {"id": 279324, "content": "早上起来看一篇日报", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1324227}, {"id": 279069, "content": "说不上每天读书，但每周一定要有三四天读。", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1290285}, {"id": 279325, "content": "养生", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1141491}, {"id": 280093, "content": "试着早起\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1176807}, {"id": 279070, "content": "每天打扫卫生，整理房间", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1333324}, {"id": 279327, "content": "手机界面自己排列，简洁清爽～", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1314503}]}